These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
City: marseilles, liverpool, san-francisco, hannover
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, paramedic, police-officer
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, bus, ship
 1. the person driving the bike is the dressmaker##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the paramedic##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the architect##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 8. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
 9. the police-officer is on the left or right of the architect##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| City          | hannover     | liverpool   | marseilles | san-francisco |
| Job   | dressmaker | architect    | police-officer   | paramedic    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Transport     | bike       | airplane | ship  | bus      |

