.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, havana, cain
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, mystery
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, july, june
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is the blend-smoker##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the dunhill-smoker##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is the person watching mystery movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar      | dunhill       | blend | cain     | havana     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | crime       | mystery | martial-arts |
| Birthday           | july       | june    | november     | december         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

