 7. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5

