The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, june, august
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, tennis
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Cigar           | cain    | alhambra   | vegafina | swisher |
