.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, magic-tricks, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, rowing, cricket
House: modern, townhouse, gothic-revival, wooden
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 2. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 4. the modern house is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is the gothic-revival house##1
10. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
| Hobby         | camping | fishing    | magic-tricks | photography  |
