There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, indonesian, nigerian
 1. the person driving the scooter is between the person drinking coffee and the person playing chess##2
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person playing chess is the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 8. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
10. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | coffee             | cola       | water    | tea       |
| Game          | whist             | scrabble      | chess     | backgammon    |
| Transport           | jet-ski | scooter | ship     | helicopter |
| Nationality   | egyptian           | indonesian | nigerian | colombian |

