.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, sudoku, gardening, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, reggae, ambient, pop
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the fan of techno is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan of pop##2
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the fan of techno is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Hobby          | sudoku    | photography        | gardening     | filmmaking          |
| Music-Genre           | reggae | ambient        | techno | pop |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, journalist, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting, climbing, baseball
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, fish, turtle
 1. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the architect##3
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the doctor is between the journalist and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
 7. the journalist is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Job           | musician   | architect  | doctor        | journalist |
| Sport   | sailing     | baseball     | climbing      | weightlifting   |
| Pet     | dog | fish | turtle          | guinea-pig     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, tram, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, badminton, skiing, weightlifting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | snowmobile | tram  | quad-bike    | motorbike       |
| Sport           | badminton  | weightlifting | skiing | rugby  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 